Two volume series, oriental setting; only slightly fantasy:<br>
<br>
The Initiate Brother  (book 1)<br>
Gatherer of Clouds (book 2)<br>
by Sean Russell<br>
<br>
and the ultimate in odd-cyberpunk sf:<br>
<br>
Snow Crash, by Neal Stephenson.<br>
(you can not go wrong with a pizza-deliveryman named Hiro Protagonist who is also the greatest swordsman on the planet...oh yeah, and skateboarding.  And the Mafia.  And a computer virus.  And Reason.  It's good.  Just read it.  =)  <br>
